name: CWNetwork
desc: Encapsulates an IEEE 802.11 network, providing read-only accessors to various properties of the network.

items.name: supportsSecurity
items.desc: Method for determining which security types a network supports.

items.name: supportsPHYMode
items.desc: Method for determining which PHY modes a network supports.

items.name: isEqual
items.desc: Method for determining CWNetwork object equality.

items.name: beaconInterval
items.desc: The beacon interval (ms) for the network.

items.name: bssid
items.desc: The basic service set identifier (BSSID) for the network, returned as UTF-8 string.

items.name: countryCode
items.desc: The country code (ISO/IEC 3166-1:1997) for the network.

items.name: ibss
items.desc: The network is an IBSS network.

items.name: informationElementData
items.desc: Information element data included in beacon or probe response frames.

items.name: noiseMeasurement
items.desc: The aggregate noise measurement (dBm) for the network.

items.name: rssiValue
items.desc: The aggregate received signal strength indication (RSSI) measurement (dBm) for the network.

items.name: ssid
items.desc: The service set identifier (SSID) for the network, encoded as a string.

items.name: ssidData
items.desc: The service set identifier (SSID) for the network, returned as data.
